HEADWORD: Capot
<hw>Ca*pot"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.]</ety> <def>A
winning of all the tricks at the game of piquet. It counts for forty
points.</def> <rj><au>Hoyle.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Capot</ent>⟦br⟧

